#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.arccosh.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.arccosh"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:1 of
msgid "Inverse hyperbolic cosine, element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算反双曲余弦值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，其形状必须可以广播至输入形状。如果"
"未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅能作为关键字参数）的"
"长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的原始值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:15 of
msgid "**arccosh** -- Array of the same shape as `x`."
msgstr "**arccosh** -- 与 `x` 形状相同的数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:18 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`cosh`, :py:obj:`arcsinh`, :py:obj:`sinh`, :py:obj:`arctanh`, "
":py:obj:`tanh`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:22 of
msgid ""
"`arccosh` is a multivalued function: for each `x` there are infinitely "
"many numbers `z` such that `cosh(z) = x`. The convention is to return the"
" `z` whose imaginary part lies in `[-pi, pi]` and the real part in ``[0, "
"inf]``."
msgstr ""
"`arccosh` 是一个多值函数：对于每个 `x`，存在无穷多个数 `z` 满足 `cosh(z) "
"= x`。约定返回虚部在 `[-pi, pi]` 范围内且实部在 ``[0, inf]`` 范围内的 `z`"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:27 of
msgid ""
"For real-valued input data types, `arccosh` always returns real output. "
"For each value that cannot be expressed as a real number or infinity, it "
"yields ``nan`` and sets the `invalid` floating point error flag."
msgstr ""
"对于实数类型的输入数据，`arccosh` 总是返回实数输出。对于无法表示为实数或"
"无穷大的值，它会返回 ``nan`` 并设置 `invalid` 浮点错误标志。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:31 of
msgid ""
"For complex-valued input, `arccosh` is a complex analytical function that"
" has a branch cut `[-inf, 1]` and is continuous from above on it."
msgstr ""
"对于复数类型的输入，`arccosh` 是一个具有分支切割 `[-inf, 1]` 的复解析函数"
"，且在其上从上方连续。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:35 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arccosh.arccosh:36 of
msgid ""
